headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Hustler
content: There are two kinds of people in this world. Those that see a Vapid Hustler and stand there in total confusion, trying to make sense of the combination of 1930’s coupe glamor with the ferocity of an armored muscle car. And there’s the kind who are already a mile down the road, flooring it, cackling maniacally in the knowledge they’ve finally come home. Time to pick a side.
